title: Need for Speed Underground DVD (no cd crack incl)
description:
This DVD image is combined from two original NFS:U CD's. After the installation the game starts automatically (no need for copying the crack as it's already done) and it also runs WITHOUT the dvd image mounted. Have fun!

I removed the annoying "Register Now or Register Later" window and I also created folder named "TOOLS" which encloses tools like - music extractor, keygen, save game editor & server/client apps for playing it over the LAN.

Sorry for my english! I know it's broken :)
